        Insights, estrategias y casos de √©xito sobre <strong class="text-blue-700">dise√±o</strong>, 
        <strong class="text-cyan-600">marketing digital</strong> y crecimiento de negocios.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Categor√≠as Section -->
  <section class="relative py-16 lg:py-20">
    <!-- Background Effects -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-white via-blue-50/20 to-white"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.03]">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_50%_50%,rgba(59,130,246,0.4),transparent_60%)]"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
